{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make your way through a land of unknown horrors, where the walls are made of flesh and seem to breathe as one. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find strange growths  and insert them into your body to acquire new abilities to use in turn-based combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166590/extras/giftestnearly0001-0078.gif?t=1732500880\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter hostile creatures and defend yourself against them with your newfound abilities in unique puzzle-like RPG combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Guess enemies' weaknesses based off their appearance, all the while predicting and negating their attacks using temporary adaptations to protect yourself against certain types of damage. Your foe begins to glow with blinding light? Simply Rotate Eyeballs to avoid taking damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166590/extras/SOFscreenshotsmaller.png?t=1732500880\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set up camp at long-abandoned campfires to sleep and dream of the world you left behind, slowly piecing together the memories of your old forgotten life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pet your strange dog-like companion. He is the only company you will ever need.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732500880","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166590/page.bg.jpg?t=1732500880","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166590/477b59c4ece850fdd0abbfadcefaa9062f29f834/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732500880","capsule_imagev5":